# Agent handoff (Bitstream-Studio)

## Language

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only — see **`communication-language.mdc`**.

## On new session

1. **`AGENT_HANDOFF.md`** (repo root) — §0 checklist, v0.1.0 milestone, implementation map.
2. **`extension/docs/DEVELOPMENT_TRACKER.md`** — backlog and VSIX gates.
3. **`extension/HOW_TO_RUN.md`** — dev stack and VSIX smoke.
4. **BS2 protocol work:** **`extension/docs/BS2_PROTOCOL_INDEX.md`** + rule **`bs2-protocol-change.mdc`** + skill **`bs2-protocol-change`**.
5. **Telemetry modes:** **`extension/docs/TELEMETRY_MODE_LIFECYCLE.md`**.
6. **Firmware / MCU:** **`TESAIoT_Firmware/AGENT_HANDOFF.md`**, **`TESAIoT_Library/CM55/modules/bitstream`**.

After a substantial session, append **`AGENT_HANDOFF.md`** §7.

